<item>
            <title>[LU-8384] convert startup scripts to systemd unit files for EL7</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8384</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Most of packages like OFED/IFS moved init scripts to systemd in EL7. Ideally we should move our initscript(s) to systemd unit files also. This also will provide more correct dependencies in startup/shutdown sequence.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
